OL,3,CLondoners wake up to 'the first taste
OL,4,Cof winter' as snows falls on the
OL,5,Ccapital.
OL,7,FLondoners received a yellow alert from
OL,8,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,9,Fas snow fell on the capital.
OL,11,FThe warning from UKHSA, which will
OL,12,Flast until Saturday, means that the
OL,13,Fchange in weather conditions could be
OL,14,Fdangerous for vulnerable people,
OL,15,Fincluding the elderly.
