OL,3,CLondoners wake up to 'the first taste
OL,4,Cof winter' as snows falls on the
OL,5,Ccapital.
OL,7,FThese snowy conditions described as
OL,8,F"the first taste of winter" have
OL,9,Fcaused school closures, train
OL,10,Fcancellations and road delays in parts
OL,11,Fof the UK after severe weather
OL,12,Fwarnings were issued.
OL,14,FThe Alzheimer's Society warned cold
OL,15,Fweather can be "particularly
OL,16,Fchallenging" for people with dementia."
