OL,3,CLondoners wake up to 'the first taste
OL,4,Cof winter' as snows falls on the
OL,5,Ccapital.
OL,7,FAge UK director Caroline Abrahams said
OL,8,Fthe charity is worried the loss of the
OL,9,Fwinter fuel payment has caused many
OL,10,Folder people to be "extra fearful"
OL,11,Fabout turning on their heating this
OL,12,Fwinter.
OL,14,F"The cold raises blood pressure, which
OL,15,Fin turn increases the risk of a heart
OL,16,Fattack or stroke and breathing in cold
OL,17,Fair can also increase the risk, and
OL,18,Fimpact, of serious illnesses like flu
OL,19,Fand pneumonia."
